
@startuml timer-uml

actor User
participant TimerView
participant TimerController
participant CountdownTimer
participant IntervalTicker
participant IDisplay
participant ISoundPlayer

== ① タイマー設定 ==
User -> TimerView : 時間を選択
TimerView -> TimerController : onTimeSet(seconds)
TimerController -> CountdownTimer : setTime(seconds)
TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(seconds)

== ② タイマー開始 ==
User -> TimerView : 開始ボタンを押す
TimerView -> TimerController : onStartClicked()

TimerController -> CountdownTimer : start()
CountdownTimer -> IntervalTicker : startRepeatingTick()

== ③ カウント中 ==
loop 1秒ごと
    IntervalTicker -> CountdownTimer : tick()
    CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : 残り時間を1秒減らす
    CountdownTimer -> TimerController : onTimerTick(remainingTime)
    TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(remainingTime)
end

== ④ 時間到達（通知） ==
IntervalTicker -> CountdownTimer : tick()
CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : now = performance.now()
CountdownTimer -> CountdownTimer : remaining = endTime - now

alt 残り時間が0になった
    CountdownTimer -> IntervalTicker : stopRepeatingTick()
    CountdownTimer -> TimerController : onTimerFinished()
    TimerController -> ISoundPlayer : startSound()
    TimerController -> IDisplay : showTimerFinished()
    TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(remainingTime)
end

== ⑤ 停止 ==
User -> TimerView : 停止ボタンを押す
TimerView -> TimerController : onStopClicked()

TimerController -> CountdownTimer : stop()
TimerController -> ISoundPlayer : stopSound()
TimerController -> IDisplay : updateTime(remainingTime)

@enduml
